  "title": "Field Marketing Assistant!!",
  "description": "<p>🌟Field Marketing Assistant!!!🌟<br /></p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for an energetic and friendly Field Marketing Assistant to support our marketing activities in various locations. You will help promote products or services, interact with customers, and assist the team during events or campaigns.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Engage with customers and provide basic product or service information</li><li>Assist with product demonstrations and promotional activities</li><li>Distribute flyers, samples, or marketing materials</li><li>Collect customer feedback or details when needed</li><li>Represent the brand in a positive and professional way</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Good communication and people skills</li><li>Friendly, approachable, and confident interacting with the public</li><li>Able to work flexible hours and travel to different locations</li><li>Reliable, punctual, and a good team player</li></ul>",
